<h2>5 · Explain Your Lesson Code 🎥</h2>
<p>In the live lesson you refactored your Pokédex app into functions. Make a short phone video explaining the code <strong>you</strong> wrote today. You may show it running. Try to use: <strong>refactor</strong>, <strong>function</strong>, <strong>menu loop</strong>, <strong>call</strong>, <strong>break</strong>.</p>
<blockquote>
<ol>
<li>Run your app and try every menu option, including quit.</li>
<li>Scroll to your main loop and show how short it is.</li>
<li>Point to one of your functions and explain what the loop <em>calls</em>.</li>
<li>Say why grouping code into functions made it easier to read and fix.</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
